var isBuffer=require("../lib/isBuffer"),Stream=require("stream"),should=require("should");require("mocha");describe("isBuffer()",function(){it("should return true on a Buffer",function(e){var t=new Buffer("test");isBuffer(t).should.equal(!0);e()});it("should return false on a Stream",function(e){var t=new Stream;isBuffer(t).should.equal(!1);e()});it("should return false on a null",function(e){isBuffer(null).should.equal(!1);e()});it("should return false on a array of numbers",function(e){var t=[1,2,3];isBuffer(t).should.equal(!1);e()})});